strings: <voice_0x01000DAD><se_low>King of tricks: And the defense is so bad! It used to be great, but now it's broken.
<voice_0x01000DAE><se_low>King of tricks: This is due to the curse of the cloak.

<voice_0x01000DB0><se_low>King of tricks: It's you princess, I know you like to look at the stars. But it's cold out. Should I go back to my room?

<voice_0x01000DC0><se_def>Dalmatian: i hear everything
<voice_0x01000DC1><se_def>Dalmatian: The legendary staff is sealed deep within Truden's castle, how could it give her such magical powers...
<voice_0x01000DC2><se_def>Dalmatian: However, nothing will stop me from being the best wizard!

<voice_0x01000DC6><se_def>Dalmatian: There doesn't appear to be any reason for the delay. It's time to show your true power...
<voice_0x01000DC7><se_def>Dalmatian: The king is back. You will be the first guinea pig.
<voice_0x01000DC8><se_high>Media princess: Dad, be careful!

<voice_0x01000DCB><se_def>Dalmatian: ...Wait. This circle limits all your strength.
<voice_0x01000DCC><se_def>Dalmatian: haha! If I get him out of here, I'll see what he'll do!

<voice_0x01000DD6><se_low>January: It means<:> Mabususa! What was this old adventurer referring to? ...
